name: Princess Diana
bio: Princess Diana was a member of the British royal family who was loved for her humanitarian work. She tragically passed away in a car accident.

name: Heath Ledger
bio: Heath Ledger was an Australian actor known for his role as the Joker in 'The Dark Knight.' He died due to an accidental overdose of prescription drugs.

name: Freddie Mercury
bio: Freddie Mercury was the lead vocalist of the rock band Queen. He died of complications from HIV/AIDS.

name: Kurt Cobain
bio: Kurt Cobain was the lead singer and guitarist of Nirvana, a pivotal figure in the grunge music movement. He took his own life at the age of 27.

name: Marilyn Monroe

name: Paul Walker

name: Bruce Lee

name: Amy Winehouse

name: Tupac Shakur
